
    fdupves Installation Instructions
    ==================================

    1) Get the tarball.
    2) Unpack it: 
    
        tar xvzf fdupves-<version>.tar.bz2
        
    4) Change to the new directory:

        cd fdupves-<version>

    5) Make a build directory and confiugre it

        mkdir build
        cd build
        ccmake ..

    6) Build it

        make

    7) Install it:

        make install

    8) Run the application:

        fdupves
